{"tid":357021,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[健身JJ]腳係咪最難有變化既一部份？","createTime":"2017-08-12T14:26:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T15:04:53.000Z","uid":98473,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7dc1fff6a5bad3db881e9e111db8fc4d0991043d","tid":357021,"uid":98473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:26:48.000Z","msg":"自問LEG DAY都好比心機 唔會SKIP <br />\n但都係好幼 只係線條勁左啲 粗都只係粗左一吋半吋<br />\n其實我有好多做GYM既FRIEND 都係點操腳 都一樣咁幼<br />\n腳真係好睇天生<br />\n<br />\n再睇返另外一個FD 只操上身 SKIP LEG DAY<br />\n但天生腳肌就好勁 <br />\n有時同佢打波 跳得又高 跑得又好撚快<br />\n<br />\n公平咩？"},{"pid":"fad18de5122b31f424ef87f6eb67db62b3f83510","tid":357021,"uid":135178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:29:06.000Z","msg":"同問"},{"pid":"0d0d45208b8430e08cf4dc9e82bd41dc82824de1","tid":357021,"uid":38604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:29:09.000Z","msg":"人地細細個開始做運動練下腳，你地廿幾三十歲先開始做gym"},{"pid":"07d078246414064fc49c23be277ac1f95b84c19a","tid":357021,"uid":62409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:30:29.000Z","msg":"應該係天生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黑人好多都腳幼"},{"pid":"330e664b0e31109ab1857b59023c09f350b6422e","tid":357021,"uid":98473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:31:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地細細個開始做運動練下腳，你地廿幾三十歲先開始做gym</blockquote><br />\n同佢由細打波識到大 <br />\n佢中學發育個陣已經開始粗"},{"pid":"dadfd6021d9b0282f3fcf9c827bcf2305c37984f","tid":357021,"uid":80183,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:32:05.000Z","msg":"用大重量試過先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab27ac3da4d19070c35a5864f155f309ade380a","tid":357021,"uid":98473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:32:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該係天生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黑人好多都腳幼</blockquote><br />\n黑人就另計啦當然"},{"pid":"3089c004