ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:39:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用大重量試過先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都係8~10 REP左右</blockquote><br />\n同4-6比差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試下大重量慢上慢落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當然啦　可能我廢所以先冇乜點進展<br />\n但我覺得天生機因真係可以話佔７至８成"},{"pid":"9dd2e8ee30edcf3d682a570f2ddbfb290fece79a","tid":357021,"uid":45613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:40:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用大重量試過先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"327ab8fda69e2f140d2828cca289e229bc07a35a","tid":357021,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:44:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用大重量試過先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都係8~10 REP左右</blockquote><br />\n同4-6比差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試下大重量慢上慢落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當然啦　可能我廢所以先冇乜點進展<br />\n但我覺得天生機因真係可以話佔７至８成</blockquote><br />\n咁可能你要再重d既機幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如:幾塊大鐵餅既leg press機<br />\n因為你做既重量多,肌肉應該會上升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa4ee0e8118bf4bad4ea0a485823339870604c1a","tid":357021,"uid":56147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:52:50.000Z","msg":"我都係<br />\n<br />\n主要用深蹲同 deadlift 黎練腳 <br />\n玩8-12rep<br />\n<br />\n練到 D肉好實   但唔識粗<br />\n分分鍾仲幼過未操果陣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7df623bed49fe144baf908171db9b283e819d5e","tid":357021,"uid":80015,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T15:00:18.000Z","msg":"肌肉係直接反映你既鍛鍊程度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇得呃人, <br />\n刺激度夠就自然會有你要既效果<br />\n乜撚野自問比心機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   藉口黎"},{"pid":"3a4c2592714c840369a7074aacfda60c1448582e","tid":357021,"uid":80015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T15:01:14.000Z","msg":"no pain no gain 阿樓主 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b12b0f69fe67f0b488d994d0595785c0a3dac9ce","tid":357021,"uid":56878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T15:04:53.000Z","msg":"點先算有效"}]}